snippet.title: Ginger Root - "B4" (Official Video)
snippet.description:
Editing films and videos by day and making music under the name Ginger Root by night, Cameron Lew delivers what he describes as "aggressive elevator soul". Combining elements from contemporaries like Toro Y Moi, Vulfpeck, Jay Som, and Mocky with the influences of the days of Stax and Philly Soul, Ginger Root offers a fresh take on the ever evolving scene of new wave indie pop.

Ginger Root's latest single "B4" is out now.
